description: Carry your gear safely with the Targus C4 Backpack for up to 16" Laptops. The backpack has a rich black exterior and matching interior for a stylish look that keeps your electronics safe. It features a roomy main compartment that includes a special padded laptop compartment that's designed to fit laptops up to 16". The main compartment that also includes a slip pocket for organization and plenty of space for notebooks, folders, and more. The front includes two zippered pockets for additional storage plus an organizer panel to help keep pens, business cards, and more neat and tidy.
title: Targus C4 Backpack for up to 16" Laptops, Black
